      "title": "A recent New Scientist cartoon.",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/23ff1b6ec78d17bbda5e0fb503fe9b41/67ca96dbccf9e6d5-7a/s640x960/e678c42aa9961a1c5518d124a6b1464ceda5f53d.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"1055\" data-orig-width=\"1500\" alt=\"Scientist type:&#10;Modern professional scientist &#10;vs&#10;Enlightenment gentleman scientist&#10;&#10;Funding: &#10;research grants and private investment&#10;vs&#10;enormous inheritance &#10;&#10;Assistance: &#10;team of ambitious young scientists&#10;vs&#10;maid, nephew, gardener&#10;&#10;Method:&#10;cautious experimenting in a controlled environment&#10;vs&#10;test on self at home &#10;&#10;Safety:  &#10;detailed risk assessments and standard operating procedures&#10;vs&#10;heavy tweeds &#10;&#10;Reporting: &#10;paper published in peer-review journal&#10;vs&#10;tell the chaps at the club &#10;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/23ff1b6ec78d17bbda5e0fb503fe9b41/67ca96dbccf9e6d5-7a/s75x75_c1/15469d3d7dbec49f8c6b7723c28f0403e1576039.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/23ff1b6ec78d17bbda5e0fb503fe9b41/67ca96dbccf9e6d5-7a/s100x200/975d43cb4d2705314561f21d94d829f11a12d75d.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/23ff1b6ec78d17bbda5e0fb503fe9b41/67ca96dbccf9e6d5-7a/s250x400/37cf7a228e86f7f4e7255fed4aec1d554ab4ab2a.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/23ff1b6ec78d17bbda5e0fb503fe9b41/67ca96dbccf9e6d5-7a/s400x600/7c8048b49a4e8fb3a1d78d9e594f98fa0cc99023.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/23ff1b6ec78d17bbda5e0fb503fe9b41/67ca96dbccf9e6d5-7a/s500x750/fbd5d0297922a5016de730f3df31c89b226eca36.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/23ff1b6ec78d17bbda5e0fb503fe9b41/67ca96dbccf9e6d5-7a/s540x810/1cc7024a6521eac396b502cc89c5058be33b5b7e.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/23ff1b6ec78d17bbda5e0fb503fe9b41/67ca96dbccf9e6d5-7a/s640x960/e678c42aa9961a1c5518d124a6b1464ceda5f53d.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/23ff1b6ec78d17bbda5e0fb503fe9b41/67ca96dbccf9e6d5-7a/s1280x1920/61ce84140f43b0f045179a72be9635e44fa4ddc3.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/23ff1b6ec78d17bbda5e0fb503fe9b41/67ca96dbccf9e6d5-7a/s2048x3072/a044ad2225a2404d13905215f709e0e1cd8078e5.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"/>"
