      "title": "A books cartoon for The Guardian  from a while back",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/2f7c1e963c6aba758a58c891bff60e25/efe0f47f9550ec38-11/s640x960/ffbc63872d8821d911b26761a0018149bf20da6d.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"836\" data-orig-width=\"1500\" alt=\"1. Freed from their labours By bots and AI, The writers wander into the wilderness. &#10;&#10;2. Living on grasses and dew, their bodies grow light as thistledown and they flutter on the breeze, murmuring poctic fragments to the flowers and hummingbirds. &#10;&#10;3. An unexpected gust blows sally rooney Into the fiction-generation district Where a robot is Outputting content For the 'normal people' franchise. &#10;&#10;4. Sally whispers something, but before the robot can open the triple-glazing, the plant's exhaust fumes have carried her off into the stars.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/2f7c1e963c6aba758a58c891bff60e25/efe0f47f9550ec38-11/s75x75_c1/2742b4ad4ffa8f7736eff34871a88dbb6bf532bd.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2f7c1e963c6aba758a58c891bff60e25/efe0f47f9550ec38-11/s100x200/e9c33168ed5b0ef469ddf08dbc1c8ee89007db9d.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2f7c1e963c6aba758a58c891bff60e25/efe0f47f9550ec38-11/s250x400/e821138b5e8c2247719bf2bd6a63fb1b04b8828d.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2f7c1e963c6aba758a58c891bff60e25/efe0f47f9550ec38-11/s400x600/f7996ca11f38b20ee4d043d42f180cfd53cf9cb6.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2f7c1e963c6aba758a58c891bff60e25/efe0f47f9550ec38-11/s500x750/ce9db2f62a2c906046e62d582ae00a3af4d90be9.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2f7c1e963c6aba758a58c891bff60e25/efe0f47f9550ec38-11/s540x810/e52e59466fcfb85f7380dd1d8ecc0a91586adefb.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2f7c1e963c6aba758a58c891bff60e25/efe0f47f9550ec38-11/s640x960/ffbc63872d8821d911b26761a0018149bf20da6d.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2f7c1e963c6aba758a58c891bff60e25/efe0f47f9550ec38-11/s1280x1920/ef28360486e419eee84fc303ae8b0432b106ba00.jpg 1280w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/2f7c1e963c6aba758a58c891bff60e25/efe0