    {
      "id": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/816239506508447744",
      "url": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/816239506508447744",
      "title": "My latest @guardian book cartoon ",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/7a5720784fadf6e812bbaa507a3f4497/191ec860c67acd18-70/s640x960/93e9c9aa60218ac1d09df3bc64fe1cf76716ec6b.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"986\" data-orig-width=\"1800\" alt=\" Panel 1 Geoffrey Chaucer, in his traditional late middle ages clothes, addresses the audience on a video-sharing site called 'ThouTube' &quot;Prithee draw near sires! I am Geoffrey Chaucer and thys is my first unboxyng vydeo!&quot;  Panel 2 He carries a locked chest to a table &quot;A most hevy box! Lete us get it open and biholde the treasures withyn.&quot;  Panel 3 He opens it &quot;Huzzah! A doz&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;n comely copys of my new booke &#xE2;&#x80;&#x9C;the Canterbury Tales&#xE2;&#x80;&#x9D;! I am ful of pryde!&quot;  Panel 4 He looks into the camera again and holds up a copy of the book &quot;Availabl now inne all goode bookshoppes. And nay forget ye to liketh and subscrybe for more content!&quot;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/7a5720784fadf6e812bbaa507a3f4497/191ec860c67acd18-70/s75x75_c1/4d882dbb0290a6faabbf132afa354068a3fa66f6.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7a5720784fadf6e812bbaa507a3f4497/191ec860c67acd18-70/s100x200/36e9155b9224e05b39ea7053a104d4cc59722c0f.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7a5720784fadf6e812bbaa507a3f4497/191ec860c67acd18-70/s250x400/1dd24805493c040c3709f13b89e3d797a3536a36.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7a5720784fadf6e812bbaa507a3f4497/191ec860c67acd18-70/s400x600/2dae03ba3dae5156f6c15cc3f22d626ad6539aaf.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7a5720784fadf6e812bbaa507a3f4497/191ec860c67acd18-70/s500x750/733b50835deb0354dd299fb99129db68be51c1f0.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7a5720784fadf6e812bbaa507a3f4497/191ec860c67acd18-70/s540x810/21f16f38ad8159af7b8adda1a64e50129f50276f.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7a5720784fadf6e812bbaa507a3f4497/191ec860c67acd18-70/s640x960/93e9c9aa60218ac1d09df3bc64fe1cf76716ec6b.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/7a5720784fadf6e812bbaa507a3f